overview: Transworld Surf has made another surf video, and yes, it's gonna be mental! One thing you might be thinking when you see the list of stars is, "How did they come up with that random crew?" It was quite the scientific undertaking. Here is the cast of surf stars we have line up for our newest release, High Five.  High performance surfing from some of the top pros, including brand new footage of Andy Irons. Airs, slashes, barrels, wipeouts... this film has it all!  Never before seen footage from a new secret spot surfed by Slater, Andy Irons, and Cory Lopez. It rivals that of last year's legendary discovery Skeleton Bay in Namibia.  Exotic big wave action featuring Ireland and local hero Fergal Smith.
title: High 5
